<HL>
   Retailing:
   This Christmas May Be One for the Books
   ----
   By Meg Cox
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
12/13/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B1
</SO>
<MS>
CONSUMER CYCLICAL (CYC)
</MS>
<IN>
