   Reporter's Notebook --
   Booksellers Pass the Word at Convention:
   The Trend Is Big Stores, Broad Selection
   ----
   By Meg Cox
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
06/04/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B1
</SO>
<CO>
   KM CRWN
</CO>
<IN>
