<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media:
   B. Dalton Bookstore Chain Launches
   Program to Spur Sales of Serious Books
   ----
   By Meg Cox
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/30/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B6C
</SO>
<IN>
