<HL>
   Publishing:
   Success of `Scarlett' Is an Epic in Itself
   ----
   By Meg Cox
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
11/14/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B1
</SO>
<CO>
   PCI TWX
</CO>
<MS>
