   Marketing &amp; Media:
   Word of Million-Dollar Deals for Books
   By Follett and Archer Jolts Industry
   ----
   By Meg Cox
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
06/28/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B2
